        " الْعِمَامَةِ لِلْمَيِّتِ فَقَالَ حَنِّكْهُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from one of our companions, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> regarding the turban for the deceased. So he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Wrap it (around his head)’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "10. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from certain persons of our people who has said the following: “I once asked abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, about the turban for a deceased. He (the Imam) said, ‘Wrap it around his head.’” "
        ]
      }
